      "message": "Spring Boot 4.0 switched its internal Jackson to 3.x (tools.jackson), so com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper (Jackson 2.x) is no longer auto-configured as a bean. Explicit definition required to satisfy autowiring in NetworkCmProxyStubController.",
